    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Armor Master's Handbook pg. 30</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> strong conjuration and transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 13th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> shield quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>On command, a <em>folding</em> shield transforms to take on the form of another shield. As a move action, the wearer of a <em>folding</em> shield can change the shield from its current form into a buckler, heavy shield, or tower shield. The wearer of a <em>folding</em> shield must be proficient with the type of shield into which he wishes to transform the <em>folding</em> shield.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>instant summons, masterwork transformation</em><sup>UM</sup>; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus</p>",
